Simulating "test/simulate/mock/allof_anyof.sieve" with "test/simulate/mock/basic.eml"
---
MATCH: allof (header :contains "Subject" "money", exists "X-Spam-Score")
ACTION: fileinto "definite-spam"
MATCH: anyof (header :is "From" "nobody@nowhere.com", exists "Date")
ACTION: fileinto "has-date-or-from-nobody"
---
Actions: fileinto "definite-spam", fileinto "has-date-or-from-nobody"
